<main class="main-content">

  <div class="main-section intro-section contain">
    <h4>Providing a community is an important part of what we do</h4>
    <p>Grab a friend or co-worker and attend one of our events, and help us celebrate women like you. We offer a wide array of social, educational and career building resources to foster a sense of community for our clients.</p>
    <h4>Information, collaboration and inspiration</h4>
    <p>Learn about investing, raising financially responsible children, or planned giving. Get information on career development, or building a sustainable advisory board for your business. Have a question or looking to network with individuals in your field? We’re here to help.</p>
    <a class="cta-link" href="#">Would you like to be notified about future events? Join our mailing list.</a>
  </div>

