            <h4 class="event-date-time">September 27, 2018 @ 12:00pm – 2:00pm</h4>
            <p class="event-description">Discover the importance of a personalized advisory experience and learn why your financial plan should be customized to your situation. Please join us for a Solutions for Women conversation and luncheon at Shoreby Club.</p>
            <a class="register-link" href="#">Resgister</a>
